&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Track Rightsholders Dataset&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;(records the label or individual who owns rights to a track in a given territory)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
